Interface Datalink

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface Datalink
extends Annotated<Datalink>, WorkflowItem

      • getResolvedDepth

        int getResolvedDepth()
        Each datalink has a resolved depth, this being the constant sum of index array length + item depth for all tokens exchanged along this link. Where no iteration or data streaming is occuring this will evaluate to the output port depth the link is from (as is always the case with the internal output ports in dataflow inputs)
        Returns:
